votebox.events

Interface VoteBoxEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VoteBoxEventNotifier

    public interface VoteBoxEventListener
    A listener that handles various VoteBox message events on an auditorium network. Events for a machine joining and leaving are included as well.
